\id GAL  
\h Galatia 
\toc1 Galatia Mite Henga Paul Lekhathot 
\toc2 Galatia 
\toc3 Gal 
\mt1 GALATIA  
\mt2 MITE HENGA  
\mt3 PAUL LEKHATHOT  
\is1 Jalenna thutah Kipana Thupha tuhchah dinga kouna  
\is1 Galatia lekhabu sung thu umdan  
\ip Galatia lekhabua kon hin lhagaova damna muchet ahi. Hichu tahsan vanga huhhingna a kon ahi ti, kichen tah in aseiye. Lekhathot kipatna lam ah lemna, phatthei taona chule thangvahna thudol asei masan ahi. Hiche lekhathot hi ajatchom deuvin ahi. Ajeh chu atumbeh a lemna aumin, lungsetna chidang namdang te chule chamna Juda te hichu Greek le Hebrew thusei hoa kon, Paul chun phatthei le taona toh thoa ajuipeh ahi. Paul chun angailut Galatia mite chu Kipana Thupha dihlouva kon'in ana huhdoh in ahi.  
\ip Galatia lekhabu hin Gospel itilam dol'a nakisan ham ti, nahin geldohsah ding chule niseh na lhagao hinkhoa iti na manchah ding ham, tijong na hetdoh ding ahi. Paul chun Galatia mite kihen-ohna tampi adih louva kon'in gospel chamlhatna achun ahinle puiyin ahi. Hiche bang chun eiho jong kihen-ohna tampia kon Christa a chamlhatna dihtah chun eihin lepui tauhen.  
\is1 Lekhathot jihpa chule ajih kum  
\ip Solchah Paul in akhat channa Missionary ache jouva ajih ahi. Hichu AD 48, Jerusalem Council masang ahi.  
\is1 Koi henga ajih ham?  
\ip Galatia mun'a Christa tahsan ho hichu Rome gam vaipohna mun lailung tua Turkey, Houbung sunga adih louva kihilna ho suhdihna dinga ajih ahi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Lemna thu  
\p
\v 1 Hiche lekhathot hi solchah Paul, mihem lhen le mihem thuneina vanga hilou, Jesu Christa Ama tah le Jesu athia konna kaithouva Pa Pathen pansah pa, a kon ahi.  
\v 2 Hikom'a sopi te ho jouse panna a Galatia houbung ho henga lemna thu kahin thot nahiuve.  
\v 3 I-Pau Pathen le Pakai Jesu Christa chun lungset le cham-lungmon napeuhen.  
\v 4 Ichennau vannoi gitlouna a konna huhdoh ichan theina ding uvin, Pa Pathen lunggon dungjuijin, Jesun ahinna eiho chonset jal'in ahungpe tan ahi.  
\v 5 Atonsot tonsot a dingin loupina chu Pathen a hijing tahen! Amen.   
\s1 Kipana Thupha dang umlou  
\p
\v 6 Nangho Christa ngailutna khotona a konna, Ama a dinga nakoupau Pathen a konna nakihei mang loi jengu hi kahin datmo lheh jeng nahiuvin ahi. Nangho hin lampi achombeh najuiyu ahitai.  
\v 7 Hinlah Kipana Thupha tahbeh chu ahi tapoi. Christa chung chang thua thudih heikoi hon nangho na ngol bolu ahitai.  
\v 8 Keihon nangho henga Pathen Thu kahung seiphongu kalvala Kipana Thupha chom dang khat seiya auma ahileh keiho hiuving ting ahilouleh van'a konna vantil khattou hijongleh Pathen gaosapna achunga umhen.  
\v 9 Keihon kaseisau kavelsei kit ahi. Nanghon nanajopsau kalvala Kipana Thupha achom seiphonga aum leh ama chu gaosap chang hen.  
\v 10 Mitmua miho seiphat hol a kahipoi, Pathen a kon joh chu kahol ahi. Miho lunglhaisah ding chu kalunggon ana hitaleh keima Christa soh hilou kahi ding ahitai.   
\s1 Paul solchah a apanna jeh  
\p
\v 11 Sopi deitahte, keiman nangho kahetchen sah nomu chu Kipana Thupha thudol kaseiphong hi mihem lunggel ngaitoa kingam'a ahipoi.  
\v 12 Keiman kathupohle hi mihem a kon ahipon, koiman eihil ahipoi. Chusanga, keiman Jesu Christan kahenga aphondoh hoa konna bou kamu ahiye.  
\v 13 Juda mite hou lama itobang loma katompana Pathen houbung chu keiman kana bolset hitam ti naheuve. Keiman hichu suhmanghel kana got ahi.\x + \xo 1:13 \xt Act 8:3; 22:4,5; 26:9-11\x*  
\v 14 Kapu kapaten achepiu houlam chonna lamdol a keima Judah mi kachan khompi ho sanga gamchenga chungnung joa kana hi ahi.\x + \xo 1:14 \xt Act 22:3\x*  
\v 15 Hinlah keima kapen masang jenga jong, Pathen'in eilhendoh a, chule Alungsetna kidangtah a chu eikou ahi. Ajeh chu hichun Ama alung lhaisah ahi.\x + \xo 1:15 \xt Act 9:3-6; 22:6-10; 26:13-18\x*  
\v 16 Keiman Kipana Thupha Jesu thu chu chidang namdang ho kom'a ka phondohna dinga Achapa chu kahenga aphondoh ahi. Hichu ahung hi phat in, keiman mihem khattou to kihoutohna dingin kakimoh no jengpon ahi.  
\v 17 Chule keima masanga solchah himasaho to kihoutohna dingin Jerusalem'a kakaltou dehpoi. Chusangin, keima Arabia gam lama kache mangin chule khonungin Damascus khopia kahung kinungle kit in ahi.  
\v 18 Chujou kum thum alhinin, Peter to kiheto dingin Jerusalem'a kaga chetouvin, chule amato chun ni som le nga kaum khomin ahi.\x + \xo 1:18 \xt Act 9:26-30\x*  
\v 19 Hiche pet a chu seijui dang kakimupi khat chu Pakai sopipa Jacob chu ahi bouve.  
\v 20 Keiman Pathen masanga naheng uva kahin jih a ka phondoh ho hi jou apangpoi.  
\v 21 Hiche kagavil jou chun keima sahlam Syria le Cilicia gamsunga kagalut in ahi.  
\v 22 Chule hiche pet a chu Judea gam'a houbung ho chun keima eina hetchen loulaiyu ahi.  
\v 23 Ama hon miho seinaa ahet u chu, “Eiho eigimbol hesoh pau chun asuhmang got tahsan chu tun aseiphong tai” tin aseiyuve.  
\v 24 Chule ama hon keima jal'in Pathen avahchoiyun ahi.   
\c 2  
\s1 Solchah dang hon Paul solchah a apanna anoppeh u  
\p
\v 1 Chuin kum som le li jouvin Jerusalem'ah Barnabas to kaga chekit in, chule Titus jong ahung jaotha nalaiyin ahi.\x + \xo 2:1 \xt Act 11:30; 15:2\x*  
\v 2 Chuche mun'a kaga che chu Pathen'in gache dinga eihetsah jeh ahi. Chuchea kaum pet chun houbung lamakaiya kiheho chu atumbeh in kakimupin, chule amaho chu chidang namdang ho henga Kipana Thupha ka seipeh in ahi. Keiho thukhat kakisah louva ahileh katohgimna ho jouse mohseh sohthei ahi ti kahen, chule kilhaitetna a kalhai hi mohseh ahi ding kanom pon ahi.  
\v 3 Chuin ama hon eidinpi uvin, chule kalhonpi Titus jong chu chidang namdang mi ahijeng vang'in cheptan tei ding ahi ti angeh deh tapouve.  
\v 4 Hiche thudol'a thudoh ahung umdoh jong chu chuche mun'a Christian kahi tia kisei, sopi lhem ho guhthima hung kipuilut ho ahiuve. Amaho chu guhthim cha a hung kithollut a eivetlhih leuva chule Christa Jesu a ka chamlhat nau hi ahung lahmang got u ahi. Amaho chun eisoh chansah got u ahin chule ama hon Juda mi chonna ho chu juisah tei eigot u ahi.  
\v 5 Hinlah amaho khut noiya kipehlutna chomkhat jengcha jong kanei man pouve. Keihon Kipana Thupha thutah chu nangho dingin huhbit kanomun ahi.  
\v 6 Chule keiman ka thusei phong banjoma seibe ding jong aneideh pouve (amaho lamkai pipu ahinau chu keiman imachomin kagel sang dehpoi, ijeh ham itileh Pathen chun dat aneipoi).\x + \xo 2:6 \xt Danbu Ni Na 10:17\x*  
\v 7 Chusangin ama hon Peter chu Judah mite lah a Kipana Thupha seiphong dinga akinganse tobanga keima hi chidang namdang ho lah a Kipana Thupha seiphong dinga eikinganse ahi ti aheuve.  
\v 8 Ajeh chu Peter chunga solchah hina a natonga Pathen mama chun kei chunga jong na atoh a chidang namdang ho henga kaseiphong le ahi.  
\v 9 Hiti chun Jacob, Peter chule John ho hi houbung khompiho tia kiheuva ahin, amaho chun keiya Pathen thilpeh kachan hi aheuvin, chule ama hon Barnabas le keima jong atoh khompi uvin eisang uvin ahi. Amaho chun, ama hon Judah nam mite ho lah a thu aseiphong bang uva chidang namdang ho kom'a kasei phong jom dingin eitilkhouvun ahi.  
\v 10 Ama hon eitem nau khat vang chu avaicha ho ipanpi dingu chu aseipenu ahin, hichu ken jong kabolnom ahi.   
\s1 Antioch khopia Paul in Peter aphona  
\p
\v 11 Hinlah Peter Antioch a ahung chun, athilbol dihlouna anaum jeh in, amaikoh a kasosalin ahi.  
\v 12 Ahung lhun masah chun cheptanlou chidang namdang Christian hotoh ana nekhomin ahi. Hinlah chomkhat jouvin, Jacob kiloipi ho ahunglhun phat un, Peter chun anehkhompi jom nom tapoi. Cheptan tei ding ahi tia seiho chun a-oimo ding akichat tah jeh u ahi.  
\v 13 Hichea kon chun, Judah Christian dang ho jong chun Peter phatlhem umchan chu ajomun, chule amaho jal chun Barnabas jeng jong chu amaho phatlhemna chun apuimang uvin ahi.  
\v 14 Ama hon Kipana Thupha Thutah thudol chu ajuilouvu kamu doh phat in, midang ho jouse masanga chun Peter jah a, “Nangma penlam dola Juda mi nahi ahin, Juda te chonna chu imacha hilouva nagela chule chidang namdang ho hin banga nahin ahin, iti dana chidang namdang ho chu Judah te chonna a chonsah goa nahim,” ti ka seipeh tai.   
\s1 Tahsan jal'a huhhing'a umna  
\p
\v 15 Nangho le keima pendol a Judah mi ihiuvin, chidang namdang ho tobanga chonsea ihipouve.  
\v 16 Hinama jongleh, mikhat chu Danthu jui jal'a hilouva, Jesu Christa a tahsan jal'a them changa ahi ti iheuve. Chule eihon Christa Jesu chu tahsan'ah ihitauvin hia chu Pathen to dihna changkhoma ihitauve, hichu Danthu ijui jeh u hilouvin, Christa itahsan jalu ahi. Ajeh chu koima danthu jui jal a themchang ding aumpoi.\x + \xo 2:16 \xt Labu 143:2; Rm 3:20; \xt Rm 3:22\x*  
\v 17 Ahinlah ihamtin Christa tahsan jal'a Pathen toh kichamna hol ihiu hihenlang, chuteng eihon achonse jing nalai ihiu kimudoh taleu hen itin tem? Christan eichonset sah u hitam? Hiti chu ahipoi.  
\v 18 Chusanga, keiman danlui kaphetsa chu kathah sahdoh kit a ahileh keima achonsea kahi.  
\v 19 Ijeh ham itileh keiman dan kajui got chun themmo eichan ahi. Hijeh a chu keima Dan a chu thia kahi ahitai-keiman hichun angaichat jouse chu kangah doh jeng ahi; hitia chu keima Pathen a kahin theina ding ahi.  
\v 20 Kamilui chu Christa to kikhenbeh tha a kahitai, ahing nalai hi keima hita louva, Christa chu keiya hinga ahi bouve. Hiti ahijeh chun tua tahsa a kahin hi Pathen Chapa eingailua chule keima dinga kipedohpa tahsan jal'a hinga kahi bouve.  
\v 21 Keima Pathen milungsetna mohseh hisah ho lah a kapangpoi. Ijeh ham itileh danthu juiya a Pathen anga them eichan dingu hitahen lang hileh Christa chu ahung thi ngailou ding hiya ahitai.   
\c 3  
\s1 Tahsan vanga them channa  
\p
\v 1 Vo Galatia mingol ho! Ipi doi le aiyin thilse lama dia nalhim uham? Ijeh ham itileh Jesu Christa thingpel chunga athi lim chu atah a namu u tobang leuva kichen tah a nakihet chet sah u ahitai.  
\v 2 Hiche thudoh pen hi kahin dong uve: Lhagao Theng nachanu chu Mose Dan najui jalu hiya ham? Ahi hihbeh e! Nanghon Lhagao Theng nachanu chu Christa thudol kisei chu najah jalu ahiye.  
\v 3 Ichan gei loma phottohna bei nahiu ahitadem? Lhagaova Christian hinkho najot pat nauva hi itidan a mihem nakihabol vang uva chamkim dinga nakigelu hintem?  
\v 4 Kipana Thupha jal'in nathoh genthei lheh jengui. Atahbeh in mohjen seh hiponte, dihnam? Nanghon tua hi aboncha na paidoh got u hitam?  
\v 5 Nanghon Danthu najui jeh uva chu Pathen'in Lhagao Theng napeh uva chule nalah uva thil kidang aboldoh hiya ham? Ahidehpoi! Ajeh chu Christa thudol kithuhilna chu nang hon na tahsan tauve.  
\v 6 Hitobangma chun, “Abraham'in Pathen atahsanin chule Pathen'in Ama chu atahsan jal'in chonphan asemtai.”\x + \xo 3:6 \xt Semtilbu 15:6; Rm 4:3\x*  
\v 7 Abraham chate dihtah ho chu Pathen a atahsan ngamdet ho ahiuve.\x + \xo 3:7 \xt Rm 4:16\x*  
\v 8 Ipi ngaibem, Pathen'in chidang namdang ho chu atahsan jal uva chonpha ahi tia aphondohna dinga hiche phat chu Pathen Thubun ana galdotsa ahitai. Pathen'in hiche Kipana Thupha hi masang peh a ana thutepsa chu, “Nanga konna namtin phatthei chang ding ahi,” kitia anahisa ahi.\x + \xo 3:8 \xt Semtilbu 12:3\x*  
\v 9 Hijeh chun Christaa atahsan ngamlha ho jouse chu Abraham tahsan jal'a phatthei achanna chu chang ding ahiuve.   
\s1 Danthun sapsetna ahin lhut  
\p
\v 10 Hinlah danthua kisonga Pathen to kilungtona hol ho chu agaosapna chang ding ahi, ajeh chu Pathen Thun, “Pathen Dan lekhabua kisun thupeh jouse juiya chule nit sohkei lou chu koi hijongleh gaosap chang ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 3:10 \xt Danbu Ni Na 27:26\x*  
\v 11 Hiti chun koima chan Danthu jui jeh a Pathen lungtona aneijou ding ahipoi ti akichen'e. Ajeh chu Pathen Thubun asei, “Tahsan vanga michonpha chun hinna anei ahi,” ati.\x + \xo 3:11 \xt Habakkuk 2:4\x*  
\v 12 Hiche tahsanna lampi hi Danthu juina lampi to kikhe tah ahi, ajeh chu danthu chun, “Danjui vanga mi khat in hinna anei ahi” kitia ahi.\x + \xo 3:12 \xt Thempu Dan 18:5\x*  
\v 13 Hinlah Christan Danin gaosapna aphondoh a konna eihuhdoh u ahitai. Ama thingpel chunga akikhetbeh pet a chu, Aman achunga gaosap ichanna diu chu akilah ahitai. Ajeh chu Pathen Thun hitin aseiye, “Thing chunga kikhaisang a chu koi hijongleh gaosap changa ahi” ati.\x + \xo 3:13 \xt Danbu Ni Na 21:23\x*  
\v 14 Christa Jesu jal'a Pathen'in chidang namdang ho chu Abraham phatthei abohna mama a chu phatthei aboh ahi, hitia hi eiho atahsan ho hin tahsan vanga Lhagao Theng athutep hi ichan diu hiya ahi.  
\v 15 Kasopi deitahte ho, hichea hin nitin hinkhoa dinga vetsahna khat aum'e. Koiman kinoptona umsa khelthei hilou chu amoh kahlhah thei pon ahilouleh asempha theipoi. Hiche jong hi hitima chu ahi.  
\v 16 Pathen'in Abraham le acha chu thutep ho anape e. Chule het ding chu Pathen Thubu chun “Achate ho” tia achilhah tamtah kom'a athutep bangin aseipoi. Chusangin, “Achapa kom'a” atin-hichu Christa kiseina ahi.  
\v 17 Keiman kasei got chu hiche ahi: Pathen'in Abraham to akitepna chu kum jali le somthum jouvin Pathen'in Mose Danthu apeh geiyin jong ima hilouvin akikoi theipoi. Chutile Pathen'in athutep chu asuhkeh hi ding ahitai.\x + \xo 3:17 \xt Potdohbu 12:40\x*  
\v 18 Ajeh chu goulo ding chu Danthu jui jal'a kinei ding hitahen lang hileh, Pathen thutep kisan jal hita louding ahi. Hinla Pathen'in lungset them ahina jal'a Abraham athutep hiya ahi.\x + \xo 3:18 \xt Rm 4:14\x*   
\s1 Danthu kipeh lona  
\p
\v 19 Chuti ahile Danthu chu ipi jeh a kipea hintem? Hiche kipeh lona jeh chu thutep toh kilhon a miho chu achonset u mudoh sahna ding ahiye. Hinlah Danthu kipeh chu thutep Chapa chu ahung kahsea dinga bou kipe'ah ahi. Pathen'in Danthu hi vantil hoa konna Mose khut a apeh ahin, ama chu Pathen le mihemte kah a palaija panga ahi.  
\v 20 Tua Palai hi khat seh sanga akalval aum thei le kinoptona chu adetsah cheh ahi. Hinlah Pathen hi khat seh ahin, Abraham athutep chun palai khat jong amangpoi.  
\v 21 Chuti ahileh Pathen Danthu le Pathen Athutep kikah a akikalna ipi umem? Aum hihbeh e! Danthun hinkho thah eipehtheiyu hihen lang hileh, hichu juijal a eihon Pathen to kilungtona inei thei dingu ahitai.  
\v 22 Hinlah Pathen Thubun aphongdoh in, eiho jouse chonset a sohchang ihiuvin, Jesu Christa tahsan jal a bou Pathen thutep chamlhatna chu changa ihiuve.  
\v 23 Christaa tahsanna lampi inei masang uvin eiho hi Danthu noiya vettup a uma inahiuve. Eiho hi huhbitna kul sunga chu tahsanna lampi ahung kilahdoh masangsea uma inahiu ahi.  
\v 24 Lamchom jep in hinsei inge. Christa hung masangsea hi Danthu chu eipuihoiyuva panga anahin, tahsan vanga Pathen to kilungtona inei masang seuva dinga eihuhbit uva panga ahi.  
\v 25 Tun tahsanna lampi chu hunga ahitan, eipuihoi ding uvin Danthu chu ingai chatbe tapouve.   
\s1 Cha le goulo  
\p
\v 26 Ajeh iham itileh Christa Jesu na tahsan jal uva na boncha uva Pathen chate nahi sohkeiyu ahi.  
\v 27 Chule Christa to baptize chang'a kigomkhom ho chun, vonthah kivon tobanga Christa chu akivon u ahitai.  
\v 28 Juda mi ahilouleh chidang namdang aum chom tapoi, sohchang ahilouleh chamlhat, pasal le numei aumdeh tapoi. Ajeh iham itileh nangho na boncha uva Christa Jesu a khat nahi tauve.  
\v 29 Chule tun nangho Christaa nahi tauvin, Abraham chate tahbeh nahiuve. Nangho agoulo ding nahiuvin, chule Abraham henga Pathen thutep chu nanghoa ahitai.\x + \xo 3:29 \xt Rm 4:13\x*   
\c 4  
\p
\v 1 Hiti lam hin gel uvin. Mipa khat chu athia chule achate neo nalai ho dinga goulo ding adalhah peh tah a ahijongleh, hiche chapang ho chu apau nei jouse chu chang diu hinama jongleh, ahung letdoh kahse uva chu soh ho sanga achungnun johnau ima chom aum deh pouve.  
\v 2 Amaho chu apauvin ateppeh u kum alhin kahse uva aching hoiyuva pangho thu thua chu nung ding ahiuve.  
\v 3 Eiho dinmun jong Christa ahung masanga chutobangma chu inahiu ahi. Eiho hi chapang ho banga chu hiche vannoiya hi lhagao thubul ho thudol'a soh changa inahiuve.  
\v 4 Hinlah aphat chet chu ahung hi phat in, Pathen'in Achapa chu numeiya konna hungpeng din, danthu noiya kipelut din ahinsol tan ahi.  
\v 5 Eiho Dan thua sohchangsa ho hi achatea eisem uva, chamlhat ihina dingun, Pathen'in Achapa ahinsol tai.\x + \xo 4:5 \xt Rm 8:15-17\x*  
\v 6 Chule eiho achate ihitah jeh uvin, Pathen'in achapa Lhagao chu ilungsung uva ahinsolin, Abba Pa tia koutheina einei sah tauve.  
\v 7 Tun nang chu soh nahi tapon, Pathen cha tahbeh nahi ahitai. Chule nangma acha nahitah jeh a, Pathen'in agoulo dinga nasem ahitai.   
\s1 Houbung dinga kichatna  
\p
\v 8 Chidang namdang nang hon Pathen nahet masang uva, auma jong hilou pathen ho soh a chu napanu anahi.  
\v 9 Hiti chun tun Pathen nahe tauvin (ahilou le Pathen het nahi tauve tileng), iti dana chu nangho avel'a hiche vannoiya lhinlelna le lhagao thubul ho panna bei thudol'a sohchang kit dinga naki pehlut dingu ham?  
\v 10 Nanghon Pathen lunglhaisahna dinga nikho ho ahilou le lhaho ahilou le kum kihei chin ahilou le kum ho geiya nanit u ahi.  
\v 11 Nangho katijat peh uhi, ijemtia nangho chunga katohgim nau jouse hi mohseh hibep a hitam tihi ahi.  
\v 12 Sopi deitahte, kangeh nomnau chu nangho hiche ho a konna na chamlhatna ding uva, keima tah jong nangho chidang namdang te banga kaum hi, hiche danho a kon'in keima bang hin ongtholun. Keiman nangho henga Pathen thu kahung seiphong masat chun alam louvin neibolse pouve.  
\v 13 Keiman naheng uva Kipana Thupha kahin poh chun keima kana dampoi ti na geldoh jing diu ka gingchai.  
\v 14 Ahin ka dinmun umdan chun neisan louna ding uva lhep patepna nato jeng vangun, nang hon nei nahsahmo bol pouvin ahilouleh keiya kon'in nakihei mang pouve. Chuti louvin neina sang uvin, nang hon neina lhunsah uvin, chule Pathen vantil khat bangin ahilouleh Christa Jesu Ama tah nasan diu bangtah chun neibol phauvin ahi.  
\v 15 Chuche pet a nakipa nau le na thanop nau lungthim chu tua hoilamba hitam? Hithei bon henlang hileh namit u chu nakaldoh uva keima neipeh jeng thei diuva ka ginchat nahiuvin ahi.  
\v 16 Tua hi keiman thutah ka seipeh jeh uva namelma uva kapan hitam?  
\v 17 Chuche thuhil dihlou ho chun nangho lung lhaisahna dingin akiha bol uvin, hinla alunggon'u apha ahipoi. Amaho chun nangho keima a konna nachom khen jeng got uhi, nang hon amaho bou najuina dingu agel jeh u ahi.  
\v 18 Mi khat touvin nangho dinga thilpha bolnomna aneiya ahileh, apha jenge; keiman nangho kaumpi pet jeng bou hilouvin aman boljing hen.  
\v 19 Vo kacha deitahte! Keiman nangho dinga naosonat thohlel banga kathoh gim kit hi nanghoa Christa lim asodoh kahsea ding hiya ahi.  
\v 20 Keima hi nangho toh tupet a kaum khom hileh kati lheh e, chule kapao awcheng kakhel nom e. Hinlah hitobanga kigamlatna hin ipi lamsanga kakithopi thei dingu kahe jengpoi.   
\s1 Hagar le Sarah a kon kitilkhouna  
\p
\v 21 Danthu noiya umnom hon nei seipeh un, Danthun ipi mong asei nahet chet mong hinam?  
\v 22 Pathen Lekhabun aseiye: Abraham'in chapa ni aneiyin, khat chu sohnu akon ahin chule khat chu numei ongthol nua kon ahi.\x + \xo 4:22 \xt Semtilbu 16:15; \xt Semtilbu 21:2\x*  
\v 23 Sohnu chapa chu mihem lungtup a Pathen thutep suh bulhit gotna ahi. Hinla aji tahbeh nu chapa chu Pathen thutep dungjuiya guilhungah ahi.  
\v 24 Hiche numei teni hi Pathen kitepna ni vetsahna ahi lhone. Numei masanu Hagar hi Sinai Mol'a konna Danthua asohchan nau chu vetsahna ahi.  
\v 25 Chule tun Jerusalem hi Arabia gam'a Sinai Mol tobang hiya ahi, ajeh chu ama le achate Danthua soh changin aumun ahi.  
\v 26 Hinlah numei chom dang nu, Sarah chu Van Jerusalem vetsahna ahi. Ama numei ongthol ahin, eiho nu ahi.  
\v 27 Isaiah themgaovin, “Vo chaneilou numei kipah thanomin, cha hing khalouhel'a, naosonat thoh khalouhelnu, kipah tah in awthong jejun samin! Ajeh chu numei chahinglou nun ajipato umkhomnu sangin chate ahaojo tai,” ati.\x + \xo 4:27 \xt Isa 54:1\x*  
\v 28 Chule kasopi te, nangho Isaac banga chu thutep chate nahiu ahi.  
\v 29 Hinlah tun nang hon danthu najui dingu deisah ho chun, Ishmael-mihem kibol hat a hungpeng cha chun, Isaac–Lhagaova hungpeng cha chu agimbol tobanga nagimbol'u ahi.\x + \xo 4:29 \xt Semtilbu 21:9\x*  
\v 30 Hinlah Pathen Thubun hiche thua hi ipi asei em? “Sohnu le acha chu nodoh tha tan, ajeh iham itileh soh numei cha chun ongtholnu cha chuto gou lokhom thei ponte” ati.\x + \xo 4:30 \xt Semtilbu 21:10\x*  
\v 31 Hijeh chun sopi deitahte, eiho hi sohnu cha ihipouve, ongtholnu chate joh ihiu ahiye.   
\c 5  
\s1 Christian chamlhatna  
\p
\v 1 Hitia hi Christa chun tahbeh monga eichamlhat sah u ahitai. Tun chamlhat nahiu chu photchen nan umden un, chule Danthua sohchanna a kihen ohkit tahih un.  
\v 2 Ngaiyun! Keima Paul in hiche hi ka seipeh nahiuve. Nanghon cheptan chu Pathen to kilungtona dinga kiphamoa nagel jing uva ahileh Christa chu nangho dinga ima phatchomna hita louding ahi.  
\v 3 Keiman velseikit inge, nang hon cheptan'a Pathen lung lhaisah nagot nahlai uva ahileh, nang hon Mose Danbua kisun jouse chonna dan ho najui diu ngai nalai tina ahi.  
\v 4 Ajeh iham itileh Danthu juiya Pathen lungto ding nana got u ahileh nangho Christa a konna satlhah nahiu ahitai! Pathen lungset chan'a konna pullha nahiu ahitai.  
\v 5 Hinlah Lhagaova hing'ah eihon Pathen'in chonphatna eithutep u chu tahsan a thanoma ngah jinga um ihiuve.  
\v 6 Ajeh iham itileh eihon Christa Jesu a itahsanu ingap lhah uva chu cheptan ahilou le cheptan louvin ima phatchomna aum tapoi. Athupi pen chu ngailutna a kiphongdoh tahsan hi ahi.  
\v 7 Nalhaitet jaonau aphanai. Thutah nung najui nauva konna koi ham nanunghei kit uvah?  
\v 8 Pathen hilou beh ding ahi, ajeh chu Aman chamlhatna dinga nakouvu ahi.  
\v 9 Hiche thuhil dihlou hi chol neocha changbong lah a kilhah tobang ahi!\x + \xo 5:9 \xt 1 Crth 5:6\x*  
\v 10 Pakaiyin thuhil dihlouva konna nahonbit dingu katahsan in ahi. Nalung nohphah sah uva chu Pathen'in koipen hijongleh achung thu tanhen.  
\v 11 Kasopi deitahte, keiman tugei hin nangho chep natan diu ahi tileng–mi phabep in kaseiyin alauvin–chuti ahileh ipi jeh a tugeiya hi keima eikigimbol hesoh hintem? Christa thingpel jal a huhhingna thu seiphonga panglou hileng koima alungthoiya um louding ahi.  
\v 12 Chuche boina sodoh ho, cheptan sah a imacha hilou nasogo hou chu amaho tah imacha hilou kisoh ule kati lheh jenge.  
\v 13 Ajeh iham itileh kasopi te ho, nangho chamlhat hinkho mang dinga kikou nahiuve. Hinlah na chamlhat nau chu ngailutnaa khat le khat kijentonan mang jouvin.  
\v 14 Ajeh iham itileh Dan pumpi chu hiche thupeh khat a hi kingam'a ahi, hichu “Nangma naki ngailut bangin naheng nakom ngailun.”\x + \xo 5:14 \xt Thempu Dan 19:18\x*  
\v 15 Hinlah nangho aphatseh a nakipeto uva chule kivallhumto sao saova uma nahiu leh kihongpha uvin, khat le khat kisuhmang tona theiya ching theiyun.   
\s1 Lhagaova lamjot  
\p
\v 16 Hiti ahijeh in Lhagao Thengin nahinkhou kaihoi hen kati ahi. Hiti chu hileh nang hon na chonset nomnau lung ngaichat chu nabollou dingu ahitai.  
\v 17 Chonset nomna lungchang in thilse abolnomin, hichu Lhagaovin abolnom chuto kikala ahi. Chule Lhagao chun chonset nomna lung ngaichat to kikal ngaichatna eipeh u ahitai. Hiche teni hi kidou jing jenga ahijeh a nangman nalunggot apha jong chu nabol theilou ahi.\x + \xo 5:17 \xt Rm 7:15-23\x*  
\v 18 Hinlah nangma Lhagao chun nathunun tengleh nangma Mose Danthua chu na mopohna um louva ahitai.  
\v 19 Nangho na chonset lung ngaichat thua nanun tengu leh, hichea kon chun: kingaichat tona lama chon hoilou, then louna, lungguh a chonset nopsah ngaichatna,  
\v 20 Milim houna, doichoina, kihotna, kinahna, kimit thipna, kilunghan khum tona, chang phatchom holna, kidouna, kibung khenna,  
\v 21 kimit thipna, jukhamna, eltol golnop bol, chule hitobang chonset adang ho jong ahi. Kana seisa bangin naseipeh kit uvinge, koi hitaleh hitobanga hing nalai ho chun Pathen Lenggam alo louding ahi.  
\v 22 Hinlah Lhagao Theng chun hitobang gaho hi ihinkho uva ahin sodoh ding ahi: ngailut, kipa, cham-lungmon, thohhat, lungset them, phatna, tahsan um hina,  
\v 23 lungneng, chule kitim them hichengse hi ahi. Hiche ho chunga Danthun thaneina aneipoi.  
\v 24 Christa Jesu a hiho dingin tahsa lungtup ho leh chonset lung ngaichat ho chu athingpela akhetbeh tha ahitai.  
\v 25 Eiho Lhagaova hinga ihitauvin, ihinkho uvah imalam jousen Lhagao kaihoina hinkho chu mangu hite.  
\v 26 Eiho kihisah val pouhite, ahilouleh khat le khat lungphatmo sah ahilouleh khat le khat kithangsetto pou hite.   
\c 6  
\s1 Khat le khat pohgih kipoh huna thudol  
\p
\v 1 Sopi deitahte, atahsan khat chu chonset in athujo tah a ahileh, nangho Pathen ngaisah hon lungneng tah le kineosah tah a lamdih lama nahin lepui uva napanhu diu hiya ahi. Chule nangma jong chuche chonsetna a chu nalhuh louna dingin chingtheiyin.  
\v 2 Khat in khat pohgih poh huvin, hiti chun Christa danthu chu subulhit un.  
\v 3 Nangman midang khattou gakithopi dinga lomlouva nakigela ahileh nang le nang kingolbol a nahi ahitai. Chutobang loma thupia nahipoi.  
\v 4 Na natoh chu chingthei tah in bolin, ajeh iham itileh phatah a nabol jeh a nalungna kim ding ahi, chule hichea chu na natohna chunga koima dang to naki tekah angaipoi.  
\v 5 Ajeh iham itileh eima khat cheh hi eima natoh chung chang thua mopo cheh ihiuve.  
\v 6 Pathen Thu kihil ho chun ahil hou dinga, amaho tochun thilpha achan khompi ding agonpeh dingu adoltah ahi.  
\v 7 Koima kipui mangsah hih un–Pathen thutan dihje chu nelpeh hih un. Nangman natulut chu aga nalo tei ding ahi.  
\v 8 Achonset nau lung ngaichat suh bulhitna dinga hing ho chun hiche chonset nomna chonna a chu akemmang thei le thina chu aki-at diu ahi. Hinlah Lhagao lung lhaina a hing ho chun Lhagaova konna tonsot hinna a aki-at dingu ahi.  
\v 9 Hiti ahijeh chun apha bolna a lhadah pou hite. Imoh lhahdah lou uleh aphatcha phattheina tohga i-at dingu ahi.  
\v 10 Hiche jeh chun, phat kijen ineipet chau hin mitin kom'a thilpha bol uhite-adehset a tahsan insung miho kom'a ibol diu ahi.   
\s1 Achaina gihna le temna  
\p
\v 11 KEIMAN JEM KHOUTAH A HICHE THU KHUMKHANA KAKHUT TAH A KAJIH HI HEUVIN.  
\v 12 Nangho cheptan sahtei nagohou chun midang mitvet a apha bola kingaito uva ahi. Amaho chun Christa thingpel bouvin ahuhhing jouve ti thuhil'a gimbol hesoh thoh ding chu anoplou jeh u ahi bouve.  
\v 13 Chule cheptan tei ding ahi tiho jong chun amaho jengin jong Danthu chu abonin anitdeh pouve. Amaho chun chep natan diu adeina jeh u chu nangho kiletsahpia neija chule kanung juiho ahiuve tia kithang-atna a nanei got u ahi bouve.  
\v 14 Keima dingin vang I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa thingpel thu tailou imacha dang sonda beh jeng inge. Hiche thingpel jal'a chu, vannoiya ka lunglutna hi thingpel a kikhenbeh a ahitai, chule vannoi keiya alunglutna ding jong thidoh a ahitai.  
\v 15 Eiho cheptan ihiuvem ahilouleh cheptan lou ihiuvem tihi imacha akhoh poi. Akiphamo pen chu semthah na a chu kikhelna tahbeh ineitei dingu chu hiya ahi.  
\v 16 Pathen a cham-lungmon konna le khotona chu hiche Pathen mithahte chena lhongpi juiya jop ho chunga umhen.   
\p
\v 17 Tu apat in koiman hiche thudol hoa hin eisuboi tahih hen. Ajeh iham itileh keiman katahsa chunga hi Jesu a kahi vetsahna maha ho kaput ahitai.  
\v 18 Sopi deitahte, I-Pakaiyu Jesu Christa milungsetna chun na lhagaovu umpi hen. Amen.   